Tightened the workspace card hierarchy with more deliberate surface, border, radius, and elevation treatment.
Polished the Agent Command header card, stat summaries, and bottom drawer tabs so the shell reads more intentionally and less like a placeholder stack.
Runtime / schema adjacent maintenance

